{"tid":1559403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有時唔敢跳閘，我決定都要拍卡捐閘！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-10T19:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T23:16:25.000Z","uid":11477,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ab25aabd3dfd2f440f5933bca64c4cddb5d618","tid":1559403,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T19:46:43.000Z","msg":"我知有D巴絲會覺得一蚊都唔好比黨鐵賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有時一個人真係唔敢，驚自己跑得慢<br />\n次次都好淆底驚比人捉到<br />\n由今日開始決定左，就算迫於無奈趕返工要搭黨鐵比錢，都要捐／跳閘！！！<br />\n收工時間係中環站拍卡捐閘，一D都無難度，係柒左D<br />\n我有比錢，D查飛狗同便衣狗又吹我唔漲，但我地又可以幫真正跳閘既巴絲做掩護<br />\n全民一齊拍卡捐閘／跳閘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b34a8c8d9c161d9762bbbd54afe1ef9b5c5963","tid":1559403,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T19:47:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5e6cd350daed6e64d0869f9530d0384f57822c82","tid":1559403,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T19:52:36.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"83ba665daa052ea3c60932bfd3f2b7504da581dc","tid":1559403,"uid":143721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T19:53:30.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"199bc392fadb87f8ea911793ec2e0a10ff4d895b","tid":1559403,"uid":181162,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T19:58:30.000Z","msg":"仲肉酸過真接比錢"},{"pid":"45e8d133698d891b430e44f150e939fc55e11689","tid":1559403,"uid":34033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T20:03:12.000Z","msg":"唔知你做乜鳩"},{"pid":"e0622d5c7d4e3a8e15f2b62a935c072e4929694a","tid":1559403,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T20:03:34.000Z","msg":"搭其他車唔得咩"},{"pid":"cb63c74878b591561f4e918ae5c33416afb2d4e9","tid":1559403,"uid":136061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T20:05:30.000Z","msg":"你po出黎咪個個都知，之後個個都學你，最後你其實係掩護緊1個同你一樣做法既人"},{"pid":"298d5daaab99b9539671e1f97b7c415fc5acdd4b","t